---
description: API route and server conventions
globs: app/api/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

Follow `API_GUIDELINES.md` and `docs/PHASE-9.md`.

- Use `createApiHandler` from `lib/api` for all API routes.
- Use `apiSuccess` / `apiError` — do not build raw `Response.json` in routes.
- Validate with `bodySchema` / `querySchema` — never parse JSON manually.
- Call `services/` only — no direct Supabase/Gemini in route files.
- Apply `RATE_LIMITS.ai` to AI routes and `RATE_LIMITS.auth` to auth routes.
